OL,7,FITV West Country reporter Richard
OL,8,FPayne meets with those fighting plans
OL,9,Fto introduce a Liveable Neighbourhood
OL,10,Fin Bathwick
OL,12,FThousands of people in Bath have
OL,13,Fsigned a petition against
OL,14,Fcontroversial plans to restrict
OL,15,Ftraffic through parts of the city.
OL,17,FThree Liveable Neighbourhoods (LNs)
OL,18,Fhave already been approved by the
OL,19,Flocal council -with a further five
OL,20,Fidentified for trials.
