OL,7,FMany people are unhappy about the idea
OL,8,Fwhich closes residential roads to
OL,9,Fthrough traffic.
OL,11,FThey argue that, without viable
OL,12,Falternatives to using a motor vehicle,
OL,13,Fthese schemes divert the problems and
OL,14,Freduce people's quality of life
OL,15,Felsewhere.
OL,17,FThe council told ITV News West Country
OL,18,Fthat it will continue to consult on
OL,19,Fits proposals
