OL,7,FOne of the new schemes will close
OL,8,FSydney Road and Sydney Place to
OL,9,Fthrough traffic, near the city centre,
OL,10,Fforcing motorists to negotiate the
OL,11,Fbusy A36 Warminster Road instead.
OL,13,F"This will create stationary traffic
OL,14,Fwith people sitting with engines on,
OL,15,Fcreating pollution in both directions
OL,16,Fat quite a few different points of the
OL,17,Fday," claims Madeline Blackburn.
