OL,7,FHer petition against LNs has attracted
OL,8,Fnearly 4,000 signatures. "I don't
OL,9,Fthink that suits the green agenda in
OL,10,Fany way, shape or form."
OL,12,FTransport leaders make no apology for
OL,13,Ftrying to reclaim some of Bath's
OL,14,Fstreets - insisting to do nothing is
OL,15,Fno longer an option.
OL,17,FBath and North East Somerset Council's
OL,18,Fcabinet member for transport,
OL,19,Fcouncillor Manda Rigby, denies it is
OL,20,Fan anti-car initiative.
