OL,7,FShe said: "We need to protect our
OL,8,Fresidential roads and if by so doing,
OL,9,Fpeople end up with a journey that is
OL,10,Fslightly longer then, I'm afraid, that
OL,11,Fis the whole basis of what we are
OL,12,Ftrying to do on Liveable
OL,13,FNeighbourhoods.
OL,15,F"We have to trial because without
OL,16,Ftrialling we will not know whether
OL,17,Fthis will work."
OL,19,FResident Matt Byrne thinks he already
OL,20,Fknows the trial won't work.
